column5: We offer a second floor private bedroom & private bathroom in a modern new construction home in the Wooten neighborhood of North Central Austin. We look forward to welcoming you into our home!  We feature: - Luxurious sheets and towels, clean bathroom stocked with shampoo/body wash. - Bottled water on arrival. - Unlimited street parking in front of the home. - Easy access to area freeways. The Domain: 10min, Downtown and UT Campus: 15min, Airport: 20min (only in light traffic).
column8: Private Room/Private Bath in a Modern Austin Home
